<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الطبع:</span> طبع الشئ, وعليه ختمه.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">طُبع:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{وَطُبِعَ عَلَى قُلُوبِهِمْ}</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٨٧/التوبة)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span> واللفظ فى ٣/المنافقون.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#707070">[ط ب ق]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٤ كَلمَات<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">الطبق:</span> غطاء كل شئ لازم عليه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">طَبقاً وطبقٍ:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{لَتَرْكَبُنَّ طَبَقاً عَن طَبَقٍ}</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span> <span style="color:#008000">(١٩/ الانشقاق)</span> ,<span style="color:#006d98"> بمعنى:</span> حالا بعد حال, وعن فى موقع بعد,<span style="color:#006d98"> كقولهم:</span> كابراً عن كابر.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ب-<span style="color:#006d98"> وبمعنى بعضها على بعض فى:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">طَبِاقاً:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{سَبْعَ سَمَاوَاتٍ طِبَاقاً}</span> <span style="color:#008000">(الملك/٣)</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>